Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:22.05,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}把对你的思念响彻远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:26.01,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}这便是展开梦想的 崭新一页
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:29.76,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}踏上新的舞台 一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:33.56,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}因为我们比谁都知道 愿望定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:36.85,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}迈向全新的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:43.28,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)\fs30}你看 梦想在此刻开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.30,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:20.01,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)}夢を追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:29.05,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)}心のアルバムに溢れてる思い出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:35.39,INAll,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\1vc(HH0000C8,H963232,H329632,H0096FA)}こぼれた涙だって いま 輝き出すよ
